OL,6,FBelgium's underage winner
OL,8,FThe 1986 winner, Belgium, has only
OL,9,Fever won the competition once despite
OL,10,Fbeing one of the original Eurovision
OL,11,Fcontestants.
OL,13,FBut the act was almost disqualified
OL,14,Fafter it was discovered she was
OL,15,Fyounger than originally thought.
OL,17,FSandra Kim was revealed to be just 13
OL,18,Fyears old - not 16, as had been
OL,19,Fpreviously reported.
