OL,11,FGeorgia takes aim at Russia
OL,13,FThe contest found itself embroiled in
OL,14,Fcontroversy again in 2009 when they
OL,15,Fdeclared Georgia's song too political,
OL,16,Ffollowing the Russo-Georgian war.
OL,18,FThe song, 'We Don't Wanna Put In', was
OL,19,Fbanned for its anti-Putin sentiment.
