OL,10,FUkraine bans Russian entry
OL,12,FRussia did not participate in or air
OL,13,Fthe 2017 competition after its
OL,14,Fcontestant was barred from the host
OL,15,Fcountry - Ukraine.
OL,17,FJulia Samoylova was not allowed to
OL,18,Flegally travel to Ukraine after it was
OL,19,Fdiscovered that she toured in Crimea
OL,20,Fin 2015 following Russia's annexation.
