OL,9,FStage invader disturbs UK performance
OL,11,FThe following year was far from smooth
OL,12,Fsailing. The contest was disrupted
OL,13,Fwhen the stage was stormed in the
OL,14,Fmiddle of the UK act's performance.
OL,16,FSuRie was performing her song 'Storm'
OL,17,Fwhen a man snatched the microphone
OL,18,Ffrom her hands and shouted: "Modern
OL,19,Fnazis of the UK media, we demand
OL,20,Ffreedom, war is not peace."
